# The portal bundle is rebuilt in the node stage and overlaid into the Go
# build stage, so the host-side copies must NOT enter the build context:
# node_modules is large (and on dev checkouts is a symlink that dangles once
# it leaves the workspace tree), and a host dist/ would shadow the fresh build.
# Was covered by the repo-root .dockerignore while the image built from the
# repo root; needed here now the build context is ./providers/quickstart.
portal/node_modules
portal/dist
